List of bugs that I found so far, will be updated:

1.} Road / Obstacles miss-collision {Wheels diving in to the road, car driving through walls, etc...}

2.} Road T-intersection near the Truth farm {Right above the farm, there is missing segment, its visible underground of the map through there}

3.} Red Patriot / Barracks military vehicles {Maybe more of them} {Colors of the military vehicles like Patriot and Barracks are red, instead of sand}

4.} Colorless Tram and DoDo {DoDo plane was white and red, now its white and grey, same goes for the tram}

5.} Elegant {Car} on highest shift gear make sound of a truck. {Also issue for taxi and police versions}

6.} Patches of 3D grass that hangs in the air
